  fhir:description [ fhir:v "Mapping of the ALIS ParameterV40 logical model to the FHIR ParameterV40 extension (on ChargeItem). Specific ParamTyp values (BMI, Billable, Amount, SLIndicationCode) are mapped to dedicated ChargeItem elements instead of the generic ParameterV40 extension."] ; # 
